blobs.dialogs.main.title: Blob
blobs.dialogs.user_settings.title: Settings
blobs.dialogs.user_settings.description:
These Settings will only affect you!
If something is broken,
please report the bug and
press the "Fix Data" button in the "User Data" category.
blobs.dialogs.user_settings.appearance.t: Configurate the look of your Game.
blobs.dialogs.user_settings.accessibilit:
Anything that didn't fit
into any other category.
blobs.dialogs.user_settings.advanced.too:
Settings which are so much out of place,
they don't even fit into
the Accessibility Tab.
blobs.dialogs.user_settings.privacy.desc: The Datapack tracks most Actions you do in the Game, but doesn't directly make them available to anyone. It also will send Telemetry Events to Mojang through Advancements(Not always though), if you have Telemetry Data Enabled.
blobs.dialogs.user_settings.user.fix_dat:
This will reset all your Player Settings!
Messing with or Spamming the button,
might result into permanently corrupting your Data.
blobs.dialogs.user_settings.privacy.part:
Change who should be allowed
to send you party requests.
blobs.dialogs.user_settings.privacy.frie: Allow People to send you Friend Requests.
blobs.dialogs.user_settings.privacy.send: Should your friends be notified if you are online?
